•The implementation of the first component of our new billing system; partially offset by
•Lower depreciation expense related to our JUMP! On Demand program resulting from an increase in the affordable device
mix. Under our JUMP! On Demand program, the cost of a leased wireless device is depreciated to its estimated residual
value over the period expected to provide utility to us.
