2018 Stock Repurchase Program
On April 27, 2018, our Board of Directors authorized an increase in the total stock repurchase program to $9.0 billion, consisting of
the $1.5 billion in repurchases previously completed and for up to an additional $7.5 billion of repurchases of our common stock,
allocated as up to $500 million of shares of common stock through December 31, 2018, up to $3.0 billion of shares of common
