In the first quarter of 2018, DT, our majority stockholder and an affiliated purchaser, purchased 3.3 million additional shares of our
common stock at an aggregate market value of $200 million in the public market or from other parties, in accordance with the rules
of the SEC and other applicable legal requirements. There were no purchases in the remainder of 2018. We did not receive proceeds
from these purchases.
